  "body_html": "<p>Fragrance Notes:<br>Top Notes: Hibiscus, Rose<br>Heart Notes: Spices, Leather<br>Base Notes: Vanilla, Musk, Amber<br>The Vibe:<br>Midnight Muse is rich, bold, and exotic—a floral scent with depth and attitude. It takes the sweetness of hibiscus and rose and wraps them in warm spices, smooth leather, and creamy vanilla. The result is a luxurious and sensual fragrance that feels like a sunset garden with a mysterious twist. Perfect for evenings out, special occasions, or anytime you want to leave a lasting, elegant impression.</p>",
